[[File:Small pouch detail.png|left|150px]]
'''Small pouches''' are bags that can hold 3 [[rune essence|rune]], [[pure essence|pure]] or [[daeyalt essence]] for use in the [[Runecraft]] [[skill]]. This item may be initially obtained from the [[Mage of Zamorak]], who provides one free small pouch upon completion of the [[Enter the Abyss]] [[miniquest]]. If lost, the Mage of Zamorak will not provide players with a replacement; however, the [[Dark Mage (Abyss)|Dark mage]] in the [[Abyss]] will. It is possible to receive a free replacement by contacting the Dark mage via the [[NPC Contact]] spell.

The small pouch is the smallest of the five [[essence pouch]]es.

==Products==
{{Uses material list|Small pouch}}

==Item sources==
{{Drop sources|Small pouch}}

The pouch is only dropped if the player does not already have one in their [[inventory]] or [[bank]].

It is possible to obtain 2 small pouches. One can be obtained as a drop from the [[Abyssal Area]] if the player has access to [[fairy rings]] and uses the code {{Fairycode|ALR}} to teleport there. The [[Mage of Zamorak]] will also give the player a second small pouch upon completion of [[Enter the Abyss]]. This is only possible before completion of the miniquest.

